To use graphic plugins, you need to have on your server :

- RRDTOOL
- perl/RRDTOOL (RRDs.pm)
- Net::SNMP

To use Oreon, you need to have on your server :

- php4 or php5 (php5 recommended)
- php-mysql
- php-pear
- php-snmp
- php-gd
- libgd2
- gd-devel
- libpng
- libpng-devel
- perl-config-IniFiles
- perl-Crypt-DES
- perl-Digest-HMAC
- perl-Digest-SHA1
- perl-GD
- perl-IO-Socket-INET6
- perl-Net-SNMP
- perl-rrdtool
- perl-Socket6

http://www.oreon-project.org/pre-requis---oreon-1.3.x.html

FRANCAIS :
----------

Pour installer Oreon sans mise à jour :

	Lancer la commande "./install.sh"

ENGLISH :
---------

For install only :

	Launch "./install.sh"

For more informations, mail infos@oreon-project.org or visit Oreon's forum http://forum.oreon-project.org

Thanks for using oreon.
